===Verb===
'''retirer'''
# To [[take off]]; to [[remove]] (''e.g. clothes'')
#:''Ell retira ses culottes.''
#::''She took off her panties.''
# To [[withdraw]]; to [[get out]]; to [[take out]] (''money'')
#:''J'ai retiré 50 euros pour ce soir, j'espère que ĉa suffira.''
#::''I took out 50 euros for tonight, I hope that'll be enough.''
'''se retirer'''
# (''reflexive'') To [[retire]]

